<br/><br/> After the shooting the officer still did not come back to his senses. He should have treated Charles Kinsey for the apparent injuries which he himself caused. Instead, the officer doubled down on his mistakes by cuffing the shot man and adminstering no aid. For this Officer Jonathan Aledda should be trialed and punished accordingly. Officer Aledda was either poorly trained or lacked the most basic empathy that a law enforcement agent who carries a gun should have.<br/><br/>Whether this was about systemic racism or just a rotten cop making a big mistake, Officer Jonathan Aledda should never be permitted to carry a gun for any law enforcement agency again.', 'Wisp007', '2016-08-01 13:37:06', 0, '[]', 0, 0, 'Wisp007', 'newsImages/dtrump.jpg', 5522, 5522, '{"groups":["Current Events","Politics"]}', 'Article', 'None', 'Dallas', 'Texas', 'Active', '[]'),
(13, '2016-08-01 19:24:05', 'Do you know who presidential candidate Monica Moorehead? You should.', 'When we talk American political parties and right activist, sometimes we are carried away by big parties like; Democrats, Republicans and rights activist like Rev. Al Sharpton, Cynthia McKinney, Craig Watkins etc.<br/><br/>\r\nAmidst all these big political parties and rights activist do you know Monica Moorehead of the Workers World Party?<br/><br/>\r\nMonica Moorehead is a leader and presidential candidate of the Workers World Party a US Communist party. Monica Moorehead is an African-American, former school teacher and has been a right activist since she was in high-school.<br/><br/>\r\nShe has run for President of the United States under the flag of the Workers World Party in 1996, 2000 and 2016.<br/><br/>\r\nApart from been a politician and rights activist. Monica Moorehead is also an author and editor to workers world newspaper. One of her notable work is -Feminism and Marxism in the 90''s and South Africa: Which Road to Liberation?\r\nShe is a sharp Critique of the US Government and its foreign policies. She is also an adherent of the Black Lives Matter Movement.<br/><br/>\r\nOn the other hand, the Workers World Party is a US Communist party founded in 1959 by a group led by Sam Marcy. The party which bases its founding on “supporting the struggles of all oppressed masses” has recognized the rights of nations towards self-determination. The party also opposes all forms of religious bigotry and racism.', 'Wisp007', '2016-08-01 19:24:05', 2, '[]', 0, 0, 'uname400', 'newsImages/monicamoorehead.jpg', 5522, 5522, '{"groups":["Current Events","Politics"]}', 'Article', 'None', 'Dallas', 'Texas', 'Active', '[]');

